# Git

- Check status before changing files; do not clobber unrelated user work
- No `git reset --hard`, force push, or destructive branch deletion unless explicitly requested
- No commits unless the user asks
- Never commit secrets, `.env`, or `.ai/data` / `.ai/logs` / `.ai/session`
- Keep unrelated changes out of the same commit
